{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"mutating","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"append","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"newElement","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:s10ArraySliceV7Elementxmfp","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The element to append to the array."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"newElement"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method to append a single element to the end of a mutable array.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["var numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]","numbers.append(100)","print(numbers)","// Prints \"[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 100]\""]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because arrays increase their allocated capacity using an exponential"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"strategy, appending a single element to an array is an O(1) operation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when averaged over many calls to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"append(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method. When an array"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"has additional capacity and is not sharing its storage with another"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instance, appending an element is O(1). When an array needs to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reallocate storage before appending or its storage is shared with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"another copy, appending is O("},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"n"}]},{"type":"text","text":"), where "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"n"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is the length of the array."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Complexity","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"O(1) on average, over many calls to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"append(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"same array."}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["/documentation/swift/arrayslice/append(_:)"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds a new element at the end of the array."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"Swift","title":"append(_:)","modules":[{"name":"Swift"}],"externalID":"s:s10ArraySliceV6appendyyxnF","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"append"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s10ArraySliceV7Elementxmfp","text":"Element"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method"},"identifier":{"url":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/ArraySlice/append(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/ArraySlice"]]},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift":{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","type":"topic","url":"/documentation/swift","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Build apps using a powerful open language.","type":"text"}],"title":"Swift"},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/ArraySlice":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A slice of an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Array"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ContiguousArray"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ArraySlice"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."}],"title":"ArraySlice","role":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift/arrayslice","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/ArraySlice","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ArraySlice"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ArraySlice"}]},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/ArraySlice/append(_:)":{"url":"/documentation/swift/arrayslice/append(_:)","title":"append(_:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds a new element at the end of the array."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"append"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"Element","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s10ArraySliceV7Elementxmfp"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/ArraySlice/append(_:)","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"}}}